radiographic_examinations.findings: Transabdominal ultrasound demonstrates the uterus measuring 7.3 x 6.0 x 6.2 cm with a 4.5 x 3.5 x 4.1 cm fibroid within the fundus. The endometrium measures 4 mm in thickness with no abnormal vascularity. A dilated tubular structure in the right adnexa measuring 3.8 x 2.4 x 4.7 cm without internal debris or echogenicity. The right ovary is normal, and the left ovary is not visualized.
